Target Support
==============
Virtutech Simics 4.2 for QorIQ P4080
QorIQ P4080DS board

Compatibility/Dependencies
==========================
1) CST is tested to be compatible with following VT Simics package:
Simics Base             1000    4.2.53       (3074)
Model Library: P4080    2067    4.2.pre67    (3074)

2) You need to export $PATH_OPENSSL_DIR before compiling and running CST.
See note in Makefile.

